{
  "stem": "22869.7",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Everybody will mourn-- oh, they killed 6 million.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I remember in 1967 when the Israeli war was, where French, where Swiss people were standing on the street-- non-Jewish people-- selling oranges in every corner.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I mean, just about anybody-- to make a few dollars, to be able to send it to Israel, non-Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Fine.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But today, the world has changed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I mean, I'm the last person in this world who wouldn't like to see in Israel peace between the Arabs and the Jews.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But a peace like we Americans have with the Canadians, where you don't have to worry to walk down the street and somebody will stab you in the back.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I'm sure that that kind of a peace, even the most ultra, ultra Jewish person in Israel will adhere to and will agree to.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But history repeat itself.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "People don't learn anything from the history.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we know that from previous stages where anti-Semitism comes up and little by little, thank God we have, in America, here, a country where somehow in some way it's being controlled, where we have plenty incidents where we know that anti-Semitism is flourishing.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I mean, we have to be on the lookout.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We have to be on the watch-out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And we have to have God guarding his-- watching us with his two hands.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I mean, it's all in his hands.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 19-- let's see-- 1951 or '52, I had big problems emotionally with my past.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Meaning, I had big problems that I never knew when to stop eating.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because in my subconscious, I thought I'm still in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if I don't eat that meal, then tomorrow there won't be any.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I never knew when to stop.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was always overeating.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I didn't feel well about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
